  <script language="JavaScript1.2" type="text/javascript">
  function chkForm()
  {
    var x_ctl = document.frmOne;
    var x_ok = 1;
    var c_itm = 0;
    var n_itm = x_ctl.elements.length;
    while (c_itm < n_itm)
    {
      if (x_ctl.elements[c_itm].type == 'text')
      {
        if ((x_ctl.elements[c_itm].value != "") && (x_ctl.elements[c_itm].value != " "))
        {
          if (parseInt(x_ctl.elements[c_itm].value) != x_ctl.elements[c_itm].value)
          {
            x_ctl.elements[c_itm].focus();
            x_ctl.elements[c_itm].select();
            alert("Mark for student " + x_ctl.elements[c_itm-1].value + " is not a number");
            x_ok = 0;
          }
        }
      }

      c_itm ++;
    }

    if (x_ok == 1)
    {
      c_itm = 0;
      while (c_itm < n_itm)
      {
        if (x_ctl.elements[c_itm].type == 'text')
        {
          if (x_ctl.elements[c_itm].value == "")
//            x_ctl.elements[c_itm].value = "-67";
            x_ctl.elements[c_itm].value = " ";
        }

        c_itm ++;
      }

      document.frmOne.submit();
    }
    else
    {
      return false;
    }
  }
  </script>

           }

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 

 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");

             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        }

        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");

             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>';

 return false; 
}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");

        }

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");

        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        }

        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");

             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>';

 return false; 
}

function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

}

 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>';

             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        }

        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");

             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");

        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        }

        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");

             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>';

 return false; 
}

function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");

        }

        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>';

 return false; 
}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");

        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        }

        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");

             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>';

 return false; 
}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
}

function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>';

        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) {

 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>';

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

}

 return false;

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        }

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");

        }

 return false; 
}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");

        }

        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");

             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>';

 return false; 
}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';

        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");

             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");

        }

             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>';

 return false; 
}

function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        }

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

}

function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");

        }

             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>';

 return false; 
}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");

             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        }

        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");

             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>';

function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

}

        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");

             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");

        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';

        }

 return false;

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");

        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");

        }

        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");

             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>';

 return false; 
}

 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>';

        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>';

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

}

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        }

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

} 
 </script>

<script language="JavaScript1.2">
function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
} 
function w31_list_screen(x_item_url) { 
 
// To Document View/Upload  
 
 window.open(x_item_url,'mywindow', 'resizable=yes,scrollbars=yes,width=780,height=505,left=230,top=170'); 
} 
 </script>

function doNDMenu(x_dURL, x_dURL_name,x_nURL, x_nURL_name) { 
window.status="Choose an Option"; 
 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>'; 
 var splitdURL = x_dURL.split("~");
        var splitdURL_name = x_dURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitdURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitdURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitdURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 var splitnURL = x_nURL.split("~");
        if (splitnURL != "" && splitdURL != ""){ v_txt = v_txt + '<hr />';  }
        var splitnURL_name = x_nURL_name.split("~");
        for(i = 0; i < splitnURL.length; i++){
             v_txt = v_txt + '<a href="javascript:w31_list_screen(\'' + splitnURL[i] + '\');">'+ splitnURL_name[i] +'</a><br />';
        } 
 v_txt = v_txt + '</td></tr></table>'; 
 return overlib(v_txt, STICKY, CAPTION, 'Documents and Notes', CENTER);  
 return false; 
}

 var v_txt='<table width="250"><tr><td>';

        }
